beer.beer_description:
Unleash Hyperbeam!

A radiant burst of tropical vibes and creamy smoothness, this double oat cream IPA turns up the fun with every sip. Luminosa hops add peach-mango lemonade, candied orange peel and more.It’s bold, bright, and made for good times.

Get ready to glow.
beer.beer_style: IPA - Imperial / Double New England / Hazy
